$interpreted: Devious: Get out of my way!
Disciple: No, you can't do this! If you pull out the dragon tooth, all the monsters will spew out from the inside. Even you won't be able to handle it!
Disciple: Is this...is this why you created the magic circle around the New City!?
Devious: That's right...I plan on sucking up the Soul Energy of all the citizens in the Kingdom. After I become like a god, then I'll deal with the monsters.
Devious: All I need to do is capture the Soul Energy near Sdorica.
Devious: Then with the help of my research, I will undergo a transformation and become the new Dragon of Creation!
Devious: But you...you've ruined it all!
Devious: Since I can't suck up the Kingdom's Soul Energy, I won't be able to destroy all these monsters.
Devious: But you will all pay the price, and I'll send you all to hell!
Charle: Just like what happened at Atlas...
Charle: So the Rib of the Snake God is just like the Dragoneye Gem; they're both Sdorica——
Rune: Snakes, dragons, I don't care!! I'll kill 'em all!
Charle: We can't let the tragedy that unfolded in Atlas occur to the Desert Kingdom! We must stop it!
Clark: Rune, you can do this. Only you have the power to...
Rune: (So this is what it feels like……to die……)
???: Rune! Please, I'm begging you. Open your eyes!
Sophie: Rune! Can you hear me!? Rune!!!!
Sophie: Rune? What's the matter? Why are you staring at me?
Sophie: Oh, no...is there something on my face?
Sophie: That's right. We need to stay alive to see each other again~
Rune: I promise...to protect Sophie's future. A promise.
Rune: ——So, there's no way I'm losing to you again!
